    "observations": "Topiramate PK was described by a 1-compartment model. Volume of distribution of topiramate was 0.518 l/kg. For a typical patient (30 years) oral clearance was estimated at 1.47 l/h, with interindividual variability of 39.2%. Clearance was 70% higher in patients co-treated with carbamazepine and was found to increase with patient age.",
